The evidence with the title 'A Senate Republican attack on animals menaces grizzlies, wolves ... ' says Mar 22, 2017  ... By a 52 to 47 vote , senators approved, on a party-line vote, their colleague Dan Sullivan 's resolution to rescind a 2016 U.S. Fish And Wildlife Service rulemaking action  ... That means these 16 national wildlife refuges will become killing fields for trophy hunters and trappers and baiters and spring hunters . 
